			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-3619142">
									

<p>Loved it. I'm already a sucker for living creatures, but the way MC&amp;D manipulates them is very logical and at the same time horrifying.</p>
<p>Very interesting concept with making the pesticide kill the future generations after the parents die from it.</p>
<p>Very logical, truly horrifying, and just plain well written.</p>
<p>+1</p>

